headline: CarMax Announces First Quarter Conference Call and Annual Meeting Information
summary: RICHMOND, Va., May 29, 2025--CarMax, Inc. (NYSE:KMX) will report its financial results for the first quarter ended May 31, 2025 before the market opens on June 20, 2025, and it will host a conference call with investors at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss these results.
